      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/11/48",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يَشْتَرِي اَلْجَارِيَةَ فَيَقَعُ عَلَيْهَا فَيَجِدُهَا حُبْلَى فَقَالَ \"يَرُدُّهَا وَ يَرُدُّ مَعَهَا شَيْئاً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3819 - Abd al-Rahman ibn Abi Abdillah narrated from Abu Abdillah (as). He said: \"I asked Imam (as) about a man who buys a bondwoman, then has relations with her, and later discovers that she is pregnant.\"\nImam (as) replied: \"He must return her and also return something along with her.\""
        ]
      }
    },
